                    role = c("ctb", "fnd")))
Description: RNAmodR.AlkAnilineSeq implements the detection of m7G, m3C and D 
    modifications on RNA from experimental data generated with the 
    AlkAnilineSeq protocol. The package builds on the core functionality of the 
    RNAmodR package to detect specific patterns of the modifications in high 
    throughput sequencing data.
